title: Grateful Dead Live at Great Western Forum on 1989-12-10
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree*, We Can Run But We Can't Hide, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Loser, Victim Or The Crime, CC Rider*****, I'm A Man**

Set 2

Jack Straw*, China Cat Sunflower*-> I Know You Rider*, Women Are Smarter***-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Good Lovin'***, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue*

* = with Bruce Hornsby on accordian** Spencer Davis on guitar and lead vocalsCC Rider & I'm a Man
